data.eml:eml: New species of Eibesfeldtphora Disney (Diptera: Phoridae) and a new key to the genus

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Uribe, Soraya, Brown, Brian V., Bragança, Marcos A. L., Queiroz, Jarbas M., Nogueira, Carlos A. (2014): New species of Eibesfeldtphora Disney (Diptera: Phoridae) and a new key to the genus. Zootaxa 3814 (3): 443-450, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3814.3.11
